com.foreach.across.modules.spring.security.acl.ui

Class AclPermissionsForm

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.foreach.across.modules.spring.security.acl.ui.AclPermissionsForm

  • public class AclPermissionsForm
extends Object
    Represents an ACL permissions form to be rendered for an entity. A form consists out of one or more AclPermissionsFormSection.
    Since:
    3.0.0
    Author:
    Arne Vandamme
    See Also:
    AclPermissionsFormRegistry, AclPermissionsFormViewProcessor
